text: "Aishiteru" (愛してる; I Love You) is the 6th single by Mika Nakashima. Billed as a 'St. Valentine EP for the Lovers,' this single peaked on the Oricon weekly charts at #4 and sold roughly 104,680 copies. # Ai Shiteru (愛してる; I Love You) # Marionette # The Rose # Ai Shiteru (Jazztronik Mix) # Ai Shiteru (Instrumental) ==References== Category:2003 singles Category:Mika Nakashima songs Category:2003 songs
